item.title: Bingo Needed
item.content:encoded:
Felina
The Yogure Village

A Note Page Bingo would be best, because I don't have Anonymous, but any sort of Bingo would let me start the Wastelands, so I'd really appreciate it. Thanks in advance. If you use a Note Page and would like to be Page'd in return, please leave a note here and I'll do it ASAP.
